28170EE2.Line7.9118B: Yes, it was my child's, and she had one just like it that looked just like her too.

5A39A25C.Line1.9118B: What is that, an effigy? Come over, let me see it!

8E229560.Line5.9118B: Well, it should look like me. It is me. I made this for someone... a child, long ago. My child, perhaps?

C20B8864.Line9.9118B: Fitting that this one has been carried back to me by the swamp, after all this time. Maybe someday it will bring her back too.

F42E1BDE.Line3.9118B: Aha, this is just an ordinary doll, why didn't you say so?
